# Create New Faithful Verification Report

**POST /fvc/v1/report**

## Description

Creates a new Faithful Verification report given an existing valid Amber attestation token.

<Add link to a FV description?>

## Sample request body

```json
{
    "token": "string",
    "nonce": "string"
}
```
## Headers

Accept: application/json (**REQUIRED**)
x-api-key: {{user api key}}
